--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: ef4120e8d7cc4784ba80e7aeb2d6d58d, type: 3}
  m_Name: TRN_3_Dialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  Repeatable: 0
  Lines:
  - Text: 'This runestone contains the ending of a story. It reads as follows:'
    Speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6386bee0cce89a84f80df160c871f056, type: 2}
  - Text: "Lawspeakers quarreled over the truth of the matter, as men asked \u201Cwhere
      does he end, and where does she begin.\u201D A man climbed to the river\u2019s
      birth, finding there no name held, neither axe nor cradle, neither brother
      or mother, only water. For the river was as the river was."
    Speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6386bee0cce89a84f80df160c871f056, type: 2}
  - Text: Bragi, I found a story of a river and mortals who debated its gender, do
      you know the one?
    Speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8b9b771dc2f105a40a7ee49c43e5d895, type: 2}
  - Text: Ah, I just might, little Lie. It is a tale I have recorded myself, after
      all.
    Speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 221624e13721edf47a3982f9e2ec5bd5, type: 2}
  - Text: Can you tell me what it means?
    Speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8b9b771dc2f105a40a7ee49c43e5d895, type: 2}
  - Text: You have yet much to learn, little Lie! A story means what a story means.
      Tell me, what do you think it means?
    Speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 221624e13721edf47a3982f9e2ec5bd5, type: 2}
  - Text: It seems to be about how people are too quick to apply their understanding
      on natural phenomena like rivers.
    Speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8b9b771dc2f105a40a7ee49c43e5d895, type: 2}
  - Text: "That is the surface level, yes, but it\u2019s also about everything else!
      Look deeper inside yourself, about what you learned from it."
    Speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 221624e13721edf47a3982f9e2ec5bd5, type: 2}
  - Text: "I\u2026 I think I am the river, and that I am not either upstream or downstream,
      but both? Or maybe neither? Is that what you\u2019re trying to tell me?"
    Speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8b9b771dc2f105a40a7ee49c43e5d895, type: 2}
  - Text: Little Lie, I told you the story carries the meaning you find in it, so
      that is your meaning.
    Speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 221624e13721edf47a3982f9e2ec5bd5, type: 2}
  OnFinished:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
